---
title: Chicken Schnitzel & Katsu Sauce with Rapid Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: Warm, tart and sweet - all words we use to describe luscious katsu sauce, the superhero sidekick of Japanese cuisine! Pour it
over a golden crumbed chicken schnitzel with fluffy rice, and watch as every bite becomes a delicious thrill ride.

